---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Engineering Services - SP Consulting">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main class="pt-20">
    <section class="bg-primary text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Engineering Services</h1>
        <p class="text-xl">Innovative engineering solutions for complex challenges.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="space-y-16">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Engineering Expertise</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-12">
              We combine technical excellence with innovative thinking to deliver cutting-edge engineering solutions that drive business success. Our comprehensive services span across multiple domains, ensuring your technical challenges are met with expertise and precision.
            </p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-primary/10 p-4 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">PCB Design, Development, and Manufacturing Services</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                      Our end-to-end PCB services transform your electronic concepts into robust, high-performance circuit designs. We deliver complete PCB lifecycle support, from initial schematic capture and advanced layout design to precision manufacturing and quality validation. Our team leverages cutting-edge design tools, advanced simulation techniques, and industry-leading manufacturing partnerships to create reliable, efficient, and innovative printed circuit board solutions tailored to your specific technical requirements.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-primary/10 p-4 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Prototype Build Services</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                      We specialize in transforming theoretical designs into functional prototypes with unprecedented speed and precision. Our prototype build services bridge the gap between conceptualization and production, utilizing state-of-the-art fabrication technologies, advanced rapid prototyping techniques, and meticulous engineering expertise. We provide comprehensive prototype development that enables quick iteration, technical validation, and accelerated product development cycles.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-primary/10 p-4 rounded-lg">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Firmware Development Services</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                      Our firmware development services deliver sophisticated, optimized embedded software solutions that form the critical intelligence of electronic systems. We craft custom firmware that maximizes hardware performance, ensures system reliability, and provides seamless functionality across complex electronic architectures. Our team combines deep technical expertise with innovative programming approaches to develop firmware that meets the most demanding technical specifications and user experience requirements.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors"
            >
              Discuss Your Engineering Needs
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>